description.detailed_description: This font, named "AIDAY PH", is a bold and playful display typeface designed by Vladimir Nikolic. It features a unique, almost cartoonish style with rounded edges and a 3D effect, giving it a sense of depth and dimension. The letters are adorned with intricate patterns and textures, resembling a circuit board or a futuristic design. This intricate detail adds a layer of complexity and visual interest to the font, making it stand out from more traditional typefaces.
